# EXP-001 corpora: bulk corpora are large and regenerated locally from the
# manifest sources (see contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/fetch_corpus.py). Only
# the README and the small committed demonstration seed travel with the repo.
/contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/data/*
!/contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/data/README.md
!/contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/data/seed-example/

# EXP-001 deploy: env-specific Vast.ai self-rental identifiers (machine/offer ids,
# API-key path) stay local; the tracked deploy/README.md keeps only generic,
# placeholder'd operational know-how.
/contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/deploy/*.local.md

# EXP-001 HANDOFF: the orientation/scratch doc is a magnet for local + personal work
# notes (env specifics, in-progress run state), so it stays local. FINDINGS.md is the
# tracked durable record; SPEC.md/data/README.md carry the public contract.
/contrib/cultural-cpt-validation/HANDOFF.md
